   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The twenty-eighth year of Marcus Aurelius Commodus Antoninus Caesar the lord, Mesore 2. Gaius Iulius Niger has paid to . . . and his associate collectors in the allotment of money taxes of Karanis, for crown tax of our lord Emperor Commodus, twelve drachmai, equals 12 drachmai; Mesore 11, four drachmai, equals 4 drachmai.</ab>
